Now don’t get that titled confused, there’s a LOT of items in this game that you can use in various different ways. The issue is, after you’ve passed LVL75 (and entered into LIT levels,) there’s very minimal things to do. You have every item at your disposal to create with, yes, but there is no goal anymore. 20 LIT trophies was a nice accomplishment, but that was finished at LIT100. As a LIT167 player, I feel I’ve drained this game of all the potential it’s had, and I don’t enjoy purchasing the same item just to Puggle it to the end, and repeat in order to meaninglessly gain levels. More trophies, an “accomplishment” system (10 Diamond Trophies for a special trophy, etc.,) anything that could add more spark for your long-time fans. Moving aside from that, if any new player has read this far, please give this game a try. It took me a whole year to reach the “end,” and I loved every step of it.

I absolutely love this game but I have some issues I wanted to put out there. I’ve recently got the new celebration event for home, and I’ve been noticing some issues. The little pewds announcer has had so many spelling and grammar mistakes, it was funny but strange. Another weird thing that’s been going on recently is the new limited time home event where you can earn items by getting keys. That part has been fine, but there’s something going on where every time I play Craniac or even contribute to my network or even Puggle, the moment I get out of the game or menu back to my home room, I automatically get another item from the limited time event even though I didn't even build up any keys to the next premium item, even when it takes 1000 keys at a time. When it shows me the new randomly appeared item, it’s the same item which is a broken down rusty car. I’ve gotten this three times so far, and even if I try to see where the item has went in my personal chest of items, they’re nowhere to be found. Not sure if anyone else if experiencing this but hope this can be fixed.
